ossj.qos.ri.pm.threshold.adapter
Interface ThresholdMonitorEntityLocal

All Superinterfaces:
javax.ejb.EJBLocalObject
public interface ThresholdMonitorEntityLocal
extends javax.ejb.EJBLocalObject

These are the local business methods of ThresholdMonitorEntityBean. This local interface is what local clients operate on when they interact with the bean. The container will implement this interface; the implemented object is called the EJB local object, which delegates invocations to instances of the entity bean class.

Author:
Henrik Lindstrom, Ericsson
